author: Philippine Statistics Authority
maintainer: Philippine Statistics Authority, Office of the National Statistician
name: farmgate-prices-by-region-and-by-province
notes: This dataset contains the farmgate prices of farm products by region and by province. This time-series includes the most recent data, covering the period from 1990 to the latest available quarter/year.
